Description: Add length, fullness color and highlights to your hair easily with a ponytail hairpiece addition. They attach in just seconds, giving you an instant new look that will leave them wondering how you did it. 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions is a long length synthetic clip-on ponytail hairpiece with layered effects and out curls. It features a 2-in-1 attachment, and can be attached to your hair quickly and easily by claw clip. Features - It is a 2 in 1 readymade looks (Straight and Curls) pony tail hair extension available in 2 colors - Hot Fudge (Black) and Brownie Finesse (Dark Brown), Top grade quality synthetic hair which look close to natural hair, This product is made from the highest quality heat resistant (less than 180 degree C) synthetic fibers, 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions can be experimented with various hair accessories for new looks every day, It can easily gel up with your hair, and gives you a perfect party look each time, Product Details - Length - Long, 22 Inches, Texture - Way/Out Curls, Fiber -Synthetic, Type ? Benefits - You can increase length of your hair by 22 inches, and change your looks in just couple of seconds, It adds volume to your hair, so that you can flaunt your looks and new hairstyle, Saves time and money, Low maintenance, Ready to go hair style, can be applied in less than 30 seconds, Easy to carry and useful for all kinds of events and functions. How to Use - Make a tight high pony with the help of thin ruffle band, Now hold the clutcher opening it away from you and wear it over your pony hiding your own hair inside, Comb a bit with fingers to get the final style in seconds. Precautions and Care - Generally speaking, it should be washed once every 6-8 uses, though this number can vary depending on your own personal preferences. You should consider washing the hair extensions if the style begins to lose its luster, becomes more difficult to style, or simply doesn't feel as fresh as before. For cleaning the hair extensions - take water in a tub and add some normal shampoo. Now put the hair extensions by gently rinsing it and washing it thrice with clean water. Do not rub, wring, twist, brush or comb the hair extensions while it is wet. When the hair extensions is dry enough not to drip, turn it right side out and place the hair extensions directly on the drying stand. Never use heat on synthetic hairs in an attempt to dry them faster, When the hair extensions are dry; letting the strands fall back into place. Then, simply brush or comb the hair extensions into the desired look. Do not brush hair extensions - finger style, or use a pick comb instead. Do not simply leave the hair extensions lying around - when not in use, place the hair extensions in a pouch/box to help preserve its shape and styling. 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions is innovative pony tail hair extensions which come with readymade 2 in 1 hair style. It is made up of Swiss synthetic fibres which look very close to natural hairs that gel up easily with natural human hair. The hair extensions are so silky to touch and feel that you may get confuse sometimes with your natural hair. It attaches to your existing hair quickly and easily with a claw clip. They are so simple to use and light to carry that you would like to wear them in every occasion you go. 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions, the pony tail hair extensions are available in 2 colour options, i.e. Hot Fudge (Natural Black) and Brownie Finesse (Dark Brown). It is not limited to just 2 in 1 readymade hair style but can also be experimented with curler to get it desired curls ( Please make sure the temperature of curler is below 180 degree C).
